{"tid":792562,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[live]  ［多廢話］曼谷芭堤雅hea遊四日","createTime":"2018-08-24T15:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T10:21:21.000Z","uid":89468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cbffece5a4e3024f172e3972769ff353f48dbca8","tid":792562,"uid":89468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"今次係第二次同主人去旅行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一次七月去左高雄墾丁 遇上打風 無咩野好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而呢次其實都係好匆匆忙忙咁就出發左<br />\n寫呢篇遊記只係因為有啲空閒時間 加上想紀錄一下同主人既經歷 <br />\n如果各位巴絲係想參考下我地既行程 恐怕就要失望了<br />\n不過大家有咩問題想問 我識既都會盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地今次買平機票 坐HX機 $1100 一個人<br />\n雖然相對係平 但係就要坐零晨機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/232739_1534262e081c1d2a0fc5a1fd9c41f8fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F232739_1534262e081c1d2a0fc5a1fd9c41f8fc.png&h=ba26e69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日出門前起勢咁落大雨 總覺得係個唔好既開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飛機餐一如既往係一個包加杯水咁 今次有多杯野飲<br />\n聽講人地食既係腸仔包 我今次既係午餐肉包 <br />\n主人覺得難食 我覺得可以接受啦 就拎埋佢果半個包黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飛行時間大約係兩小時四十五分鐘左右啦<br />\n曼谷時間朝早兩點半就落機 <br />\n用左好多時間係到hea行 同埋慢慢咁寫入境表果張野 出到黎已經朝早四點啦<br />\n<br />\n事前我係中環百年唱左錢 匯率大約1:4.1 我唱左好小 純粹係for Day1 因為到埗太早 機場最平既super rich朝早六點先開 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233055_72257b19be3d113bf18aea1d4ee8fece.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233055_72257b19be3d113bf18aea1d4ee8fece.png&h=9ffdc0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有係機場買左sim card 299B <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233151_5425384f1e7d970dc4256b7dcc3d99aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233151_5425384f1e7d970dc4256b7dcc3d99aa.png&h=e35116d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主人驚我覺得太攰 唔想我訓機場 就book左間機場附近既酒店訓一教 起身先再去芭堤雅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地第一間酒店個名叫 At residence suvarnabhumi $305 <br />\n$ 呢間酒店性價比我比7/10啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係搵過咁多間機場附近酒店 既價錢接受到得黎又評價好好既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233246_4991613a4517d7504e02373b64c66bcc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233246_4991613a4517d7504e02373b64c66bcc.png&h=598cdb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返先 我地今次book既酒店係用agoda <br />\n酒店位置離機場大約10分鐘左右<br />\n機場B1成層都係transportation  有分短長程的士 去到counter 你比地址佢睇 佢就會幫你安排邊架的士 記住跟咪錶計 額外加50B比個司機做小費 <br />\n題外話：好多人都話要down GRAB 好好用 但係去到芭堤雅就一般啦 唔知曼谷果邊需唔需要用呢 （如果用Grab由機場去酒店要150B 但係直接counter order 比錢就120B咋）<br />\n<br />\nCheck in 之後就同主人快快手沖個靚涼就訓教啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間酒店唔可以話恐怖 但心理作用下成日覺得聽到聲咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過主人話完全無聲 <br />\n<br />\n起身9點食個早餐 90B 麥片好伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過整體上都接受到既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233350_a9eea1945b5e89130dfe87e44e62ff9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233350_a9eea1945b5e89130dfe87e44e62ff9c.png&h=9aa3325d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233355_52aadbf51ace8dfd281676d11f21da22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233355_52aadbf51ace8dfd281676d11f21da22.png&h=3a59e01e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後同酒店check out 佢會幫你叫埋的士 <br />\n返機場咪錶80B左右 不過我地都照比左120B 當小費啦<br />\n<br />\n到左機場 就即刻去左買去芭堤雅既巴士票 122B一個人<br />\n同一層有個food court 勁多人 野食都唔差既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233723_8886d747a8b66ecc4445eb89d6330bea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233723_8886d747a8b66ecc4445eb89d6330bea.png&h=510999fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233752_aa1d6942b17ee17f51d537dc95e0244e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233752_aa1d6942b17ee17f51d537dc95e0244e.png&h=7c6d66b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去芭堤雅仲有其他車 但係就貴啦 我地就簡左最平又安全既方法 btw 如果行李超過20kg 要比多20B <br />\n車程大約2個半鐘就到啦 訓訓下其實好快 座位又夠闊夠軟又乾淨過大陸啲長途巴十倍<br />\n<br />\n建議大家去前search下邊個站近自己既酒店 我同主人簡果間就近第一個站 之後再轉泰國好出名既嘟嘟車 300B/2ppl 係貴左啲 但唔緊要啦 我地成個trip都無講過價 接受到個價錢就得<br />\n<br />\n芭堤雅間酒店叫Hotel Mera  Mare Pattaya $1112 2night<br />\n呢到有一個細細既泳池 同gym room <br />\nCP值都高既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233457_34cf86a17df853c438139500c98bcb19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233457_34cf86a17df853c438139500c98bcb19.png&h=6120d91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地擺低行李就向右行15分鐘左右 就到左central marina <br />\n講一講先 central marina 附近有好多local tour 我地是但報左間 睇69成人秀 同 第二日既水上活動 分別係1500B同1650B一個人 活動都會有司機車你去 自己搵車返 <br />\nbook左六半既成人秀就去左行一陣central marina人面個big c <br />\n但係其實曼谷都有大把 我就唔會係到買返去啦 big C出面有啲賣衫呀小手作既地方 我係呢到都買左件背心仔 100B好抵"},{"pid":"40c4547dad47ddb53520d49c2042a1dd83282b4b","tid":792562,"uid":89468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"Central marina係幾值得去既 對面有啲大浴場酒吧果啲 主人有我都唔洗去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過聽講價錢唔貴 有興趣既巴打可以去睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/233915_983f21622a474e60e7116ebc16663dac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F233915_983f21622a474e60e7116ebc16663dac.png&h=327c40c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCentral marina 出面有啲賣野食既攤檔 都唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/234017_3238e98ae8ac1adbb3a3c382af4f9ca7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F234017_3238e98ae8ac1adbb3a3c382af4f9ca7.png&h=112f477b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就69成人秀 我第一次睇呢啲咁既表演 好新奇 但都幾貴下 比我簡多次我唔會睇 成個表演一個鐘左右 佢唔會趕你走 坐第一排有得揸波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有得舔啲女既波 有啲環節會簡第一排既觀眾上去 會有兩個裸女夾住你咁 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲係免費 唔洗額外加錢 所以各位巴絲記得要狗衝去第一排中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完69成人秀其實已經好攰就返左central marina行街食下飯咁 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/234059_ab71e847d94b21726b1e62ee284e251e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F234059_ab71e847d94b21726b1e62ee284e251e.png&h=b031e6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/234103_93f325efb1a7814157df1eecfb09c9bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F234103_93f325efb1a7814157df1eecfb09c9bd.png&h=a2134ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/234107_a3b0f9fe06f75be1b182b45143fa8ae9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F234107_a3b0f9fe06f75be1b182b45143fa8ae9.png&h=ee431d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBig C買既mango 唔好食。<br />\n<br />\n仲食左個m記 貴得黎又難食 都係香港好<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/234239_918b52401b296fff28c56270523776fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F234239_918b52401b296fff28c56270523776fc.png&h=6353caf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一日就咁完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二日就會去玩水上活動#<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a709695e84401adc405bd17e8aee490695fa03","tid":792562,"uid":32353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"失左蹤？"},{"pid":"ed404fc4a550beb17f4dae972ea37d6d4f6a5833","tid":792562,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2a709695e84401adc405bd17e8aee490695fa03","tid":792562,"uid":32353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"失左蹤？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b8cac3ca69ad94e8e15bd43e7cb72a9bebbdbf","tid":792562,"uid":86651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"想睇"},{"pid":"04f61cdaf8846823a00d8d57a5af5419c4595234","tid":792562,"uid":132857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:39:33.000Z","msg":"打埋落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a8bfb521b6e357e71c7a02cd0f76f1466a5e6a","tid":792562,"uid":147159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:21:21.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以介紹下程巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}